  "detailed_description": "<strong>We hope that more friends who love this type of game can participate in the trial and give any feedback on the game. Your support is the biggest motivation for the team! grateful</strong><br><strong>discord： </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/a4b0ae7bfe68fef8a38c066c120a02c8.avif?t=1753847222\" width=620 height=76 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/f0a7d7ac4f5f3808cc1fbd9b7fdb9478.poster.avif?t=1753847222\" width=614 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/f0a7d7ac4f5f3808cc1fbd9b7fdb9478.webm?t=1753847222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/f0a7d7ac4f5f3808cc1fbd9b7fdb9478.mp4?t=1753847222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Welcome to a seafaring world full of adventure and wonder!<br>Here you are free to pilot your ship and explore the endless oceans in search of hidden islands and treasures!<br>You can follow the clues of treasure maps, solve ancient puzzles, and discover lost civilizations and riches!<br>You can also engage in fierce sea battles with pirates, defeating them and capturing their loot!<br>You can also trade between islands, acquire islands, and build your own trade network! </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/1054afabb0c5349ae08a9f1c0102f1a1.avif?t=1753847222\" width=620 height=76 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/f90306094b2c2498680f1a9fa805349a.poster.avif?t=1753847222\" width=614 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/f90306094b2c2498680f1a9fa805349a.webm?t=1753847222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/f90306094b2c2498680f1a9fa805349a.mp4?t=1753847222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>This is a vast sea full of opportunities and challenges.<br>You'll need to build your own fleet, travel between ports, kill pirates or plunder merchant ships.<br>Fortunately, there are also many friendly merchants and ports here.<br>You can trade with them and buy or sell various items and information.<br>You can trade the treasures you find at sea or on the island for gold or equipment. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/9d3cf929f511fabb64f2d005ab2b58b6.avif?t=1753847222\" width=620 height=76 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/e90286f4e6821d1307c5910167902595.poster.avif?t=1753847222\" width=614 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/e90286f4e6821d1307c5910167902595.webm?t=1753847222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/e90286f4e6821d1307c5910167902595.mp4?t=1753847222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Here, you can be both the bounty hunter and the hunted.<br>If you want to fight for justice, you can accept bounty missions issued by the Navy and hunt down those notorious pirate leaders.<br>If you want to fight for freedom, you can challenge the navy and other forces to become the most powerful pirate king.<br>But no matter what, when you rise to fame, you will be targeted!<br>Only death will free you from everyone! </strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>We hope that more friends who love this type of game can participate in the trial and give any feedback on the game. Your support is the biggest motivation for the team! grateful</strong><br><strong>discord： </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/a4b0ae7bfe68fef8a38c066c120a02c8.avif?t=1753847222\" width=620 height=76 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/f0a7d7ac4f5f3808cc1fbd9b7fdb9478.poster.avif?t=1753847222\" width=614 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/f0a7d7ac4f5f3808cc1fbd9b7fdb9478.webm?t=1753847222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/f0a7d7ac4f5f3808cc1fbd9b7fdb9478.mp4?t=1753847222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Welcome to a seafaring world full of adventure and wonder!<br>Here you are free to pilot your ship and explore the endless oceans in search of hidden islands and treasures!<br>You can follow the clues of treasure maps, solve ancient puzzles, and discover lost civilizations and riches!<br>You can also engage in fierce sea battles with pirates, defeating them and capturing their loot!<br>You can also trade between islands, acquire islands, and build your own trade network! </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/1054afabb0c5349ae08a9f1c0102f1a1.avif?t=1753847222\" width=620 height=76 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/f90306094b2c2498680f1a9fa805349a.poster.avif?t=1753847222\" width=614 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/f90306094b2c2498680f1a9fa805349a.webm?t=1753847222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/f90306094b2c2498680f1a9fa805349a.mp4?t=1753847222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>This is a vast sea full of opportunities and challenges.<br>You'll need to build your own fleet, travel between ports, kill pirates or plunder merchant ships.<br>Fortunately, there are also many friendly merchants and ports here.<br>You can trade with them and buy or sell various items and information.<br>You can trade the treasures you find at sea or on the island for gold or equipment. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/9d3cf929f511fabb64f2d005ab2b58b6.avif?t=1753847222\" width=620 height=76 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/e90286f4e6821d1307c5910167902595.poster.avif?t=1753847222\" width=614 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/e90286f4e6821d1307c5910167902595.webm?t=1753847222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137240/extras/e90286f4e6821d1307c5910167902595.mp4?t=1753847222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Here, you can be both the bounty hunter and the hunted.<br>If you want to fight for justice, you can accept bounty missions issued by the Navy and hunt down those notorious pirate leaders.<br>If you want to fight for freedom, you can challenge the navy and other forces to become the most powerful pirate king.<br>But no matter what, when you rise to fame, you will be targeted!<br>Only death will free you from everyone! </strong>",
